  • Method Details

    • uiReadyEvaluation

      public static EvaluationBuilder uiReadyEvaluation(Currency currency)
      Creates a new, ui ready, EvaluationBuilder with the following fields set
      • Claim - if a claim is specified via onClaim or by using claimBuilder.withEvaluation then use the specified claim. Otherwise a new ui ready auto claim is created.
      • Name - set to unique title of the form NameN
      • Amount - set to 200 (override using withAmount() if this is not suitable) with the provided currency.
        Parameters:
        currency - the currency for the amount
        Returns:
        a new ui ready builder

      • uiReadyEvaluation

        public static EvaluationBuilder uiReadyEvaluation(CurrencyAmount amount)
        Creates a new, ui ready, EvaluationBuilder with the following fields set
        • Claim - if a claim is specified via onClaim or by using claimBuilder.withEvaluation then use the specified claim. Otherwise a new ui ready auto claim is created.
        • Name - set to unique title of the form NameN
          Parameters:
          amount - the total evaluation amount
          Returns:
          a new ui ready builder
